videoData.title: Why I don't like Victorian Literature | The Woman in White by Wilkie Collins
videoData.description: Hello I don't like this era of books BUT I do like complaining about them. TWIW was genuinely good but resparked a lot of my Victorian frustrations.
videoData.quote: I will give you some tea to compose your spirits, and do all a woman can (which is very little, by-the-by) to hold my tongue
